import pandas as pd
import numpy as np

def entance(dfh, symmop):
    positions = dfh[['x', 'y', 'z']].to_numpy()
    rotated_positions = np.dot(positions, symmop)
    dfh[['', 'y', 'z']] = rotated_positions
    return dfh
